---
title: "Learn agentic AI"
description: "Practical guides for getting the most out of agentic AI. Cost breakdowns, best skills, use cases, and deep dives."
permalink: /learn/
---
{% extends "base.njk" %}

{% block styles %}
  .learn-hero { padding: 64px 0 44px; text-align: center; }
  .learn-hero-pre { font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--accent); letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .learn-hero h1 { font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3rem); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin-bottom: 14px; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.05; }
  .learn-hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 500; }
  .learn-hero p { font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--ink-soft); max-width: 540px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.6; }

  .guides-grid { display: grid; gap: 14px; margin-bottom: 80px; max-width: 760px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
  .guide-card { display: block; text-decoration: none; color: inherit; padding: 24px 26px; border-radius: 14px; border: 1px solid var(--rule); background: var(--paper); transition: all 0.2s; }
  .guide-card:hover { border-color: var(--accent); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(21, 36, 61, 0.07); }
  .guide-card-meta { font-size: 0.74rem; color: var(--ink-mute); margin-bottom: 10px; display: flex; gap: 14px; }
  .guide-card h2 { font-family: 'Fraunces', serif; font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.01em; margin-bottom: 8px; color: var(--ink); line-height: 1.3; }
  .guide-card p { font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--ink-soft); line-height: 1.55; }
{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
  <div class="container-wide">
    <section class="learn-hero">
      <div class="learn-hero-pre">Learn</div>
      <h1>Learn <em>agentic AI</em></h1>
      <p>Practical guides from people who use agentic AI every day. No fluff, no theory. Just what works.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="guides-grid">
      {% for post in collections.learn %}
        <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="guide-card">
          <div class="guide-card-meta">
            {% if post.data.readTime %}<span>📖 {{ post.data.readTime }}</span>{% endif %}
            {% if post.data.lastUpdated %}<span>Updated {{ post.data.lastUpdated }}</span>{% endif %}
          </div>
          <h2>{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
          <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        </a>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
{% endblock %}
